Package: ribex
Type: Package
Title: R Interface for Ibex
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Ibex", "Developers", email = "ibex@example.invalid", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Pure-R bindings for the Ibex dataframe DSL. Queries are parsed and
    executed by the Ibex C++ runtime and results are imported into R through the
    Arrow C Data Interface using nanoarrow. Results can be returned as a nanoarrow
    array or converted directly to a data.frame for immediate use with ggplot2.
Depends: R (>= 4.4)
Imports:
    nanoarrow
SystemRequirements: C++23, an existing Ibex build tree
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
